by using the app you are already accepting privacy policy !
Information We Collect

Personal Information: Name, contact details, delivery address.

Location Data: GPS location (only when delivery is requested).

How We Use Information

To process and deliver your order.

To improve our services and app experience.

Sharing of Data

We do not sell or rent your information.

Data may be shared with delivery staff solely to complete your order.

Data Security
We use reasonable security measures to protect your data, but we cannot guarantee 100% security.

User Rights
You may request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data by contacting us at abdrhmanbnyahya1@gmail.com


Location Data
Location is collected only when needed for delivery and is not stored longer than necessary.

Updates to this Policy
We may update these policies occasionally. Continued use of the app means acceptance of any changes.
